org.llrp.ltk.generated.parameters

Class AISpecStopTrigger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.llrp.ltk.types.LLRPParameter
      • org.llrp.ltk.types.TLVParameter
        • org.llrp.ltk.generated.parameters.AISpecStopTrigger

  • public class AISpecStopTrigger
extends TLVParameter
    This parameter defines the stop (i.e., terminating boundary) of an antenna inventory operation. See also LLRP Specification Section 10.2.2.1 and LLRP Specification Section 16.2.4.2.1 .
